'''安德鲁·大卫·萨姆伯格'''（一般被称作'''安迪·萨姆伯格'''，{{lang-en|'''Andrew David "Andy" Samberg'''}}，{{bd|1978年|8月18日}}）<ref name=birthrecord />是一位美国演员、单口喜剧演员、编剧，[[艾美奖|艾美奖]]和[[金球奖|金球奖]]得主，是喜剧团体{{link-en|寂寞孤岛乐队|The Lonely Island}}的成员。萨姆伯格在2005年到2012年期间担任喜剧节目《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》的演员，并因此而成名。他为这档节目创立了“{{link-en|周六夜现场数码短片|SNL Digital Shorts}}”的环节，并使其广受欢迎。这一环节主要是他与节目的其他演员共同主演的喜剧短片或音乐录影带。<ref name="Daily News New York">{{cite news|last=|first=|title=2007 Emmy Winners: The complete list|publisher=[[紐約每日新聞|''Daily News'' (New York)]]|date=17 September 2007|url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv/2007/09/17/2007-09-17_2007_emmy_winners_the_complete_list.html?page=0|accessdate=December 22, 2008|archive-date=2009-03-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090305213510/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/tv/2007/09/17/2007-09-17_2007_emmy_winners_the_complete_list.html?page=0|dead-url=no}}</ref>萨姆伯格还主演了《{{link-en|飞车手罗德|Hot Rod (film)}}》、《[[尋找伴郎|尋找伴郎]]》、《[[精灵旅社|精灵旅社]]》、《[[爸爸的好儿子|爸爸的好儿子]]》和《{{link-en|离婚不分手|Celeste and Jesse Forever}}》等电影。2013年起，他开始主演自己制作的情景喜剧《[[荒唐分局|荒唐分局]]》，并凭借在剧中的表演在2014年初获得[[金球奖|金球奖]]。

==早年生活==
萨姆伯格出生于美国[[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[伯克利|伯克利]]。他的母亲玛乔丽·“玛姬”（{{lang|en|Marjorie "Margi"}}）婚前本姓麦罗（{{lang|en|Marrow}}），是一位小学教师，父亲乔则是一位摄影师。<ref name="parents">{{cite news|last=Grant|first=Lee|coauthors=|title=The three amigos|pages=|publisher=SignOnSanDiego|date=August 3, 2007|url=http://www.signonsandiego.com/news/features/20070803-9999-lz1c03hotrod.html|accessdate=August 6, 2007|archive-date=2007-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071011171002/http://www.signonsandiego.com/news/features/20070803-9999-lz1c03hotrod.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>他有两个姐妹，乔安娜（{{lang|en|Johanna}}）和达萝（{{lang|en|Darrow}}）。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.hollywood.com/celebrity/3488975/Andy_Samberg_Biography |title=Andy Samberg Biography | Family, Companions |publisher=Hollywood.com |date= |accessdate=2012-02-16 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120908201456/http://www.hollywood.com/celebrity/3488975/Andy_Samberg_Biography |archivedate=2012-09-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>萨姆伯格一家有[[犹太人|犹太]]血统，其外祖父{{link-en|阿尔弗雷德·麦罗|Alfred J. Marrow}}是一位[[工業與組織心理學|工业心理学家]]和慈善家，曾任{{link-en|美国犹太人大会|American Jewish Congress}}执行主席。然而萨姆伯格曾表示自己“没有特别的宗教信仰”。<ref name="Samberg1">{{cite news| last=Bloom| first=Nate| title=Celebrity Jews| date=August 2, 2007| url=http://www.jewishsf.com/content/2-0-/module/displaystory/story_id/33176/format/html/displaystory.html| accessdate=August 6, 2007| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070930030448/http://www.jewishsf.com/content/2-0-/module/displaystory/story_id/33176/format/html/displaystory.html| archive-date=2007-09-30| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name=schooze>[http://www.schmoozemag.com/?p=744 "Q&A with Andy Samberg: Meet the creative genius"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.schmoozemag.com/?p=744 |date=20110716014010 }}, schmoozemag.com, 9 November 2008; retrieved 14 May 2009.</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://timeoutchicago.com/arts-culture/film/15426341/andy-samberg-interview|title=Andy Samberg<nowiki>|</nowiki> Interview|publisher=Time Out Chicago|date=2012-06-14|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015230313/http://www.timeoutchicago.com/arts-culture/film/15426341/andy-samberg-interview|archivedate=2013-10-15|access-date=2014-02-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

萨姆伯格年幼时一次悄悄瞒着父母在电视上看职业摔跤比赛时偶然发现了《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》这档节目，此后便为之深深着迷。而他热衷喜剧，无法专心学习，也让他的老师十分不满。<ref name="Gainesville Sun">{{cite web|url=http://www.gainesville.com/article/20100323/articles/100329755|title=Andy Samberg starting yearning for 'SNL' at about age 8|last=Crabbe|first=Nathan|work=The Gainesville Sun|date=March 23, 2010|accessdate=January 16, 2011|archive-date=2016-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160413151158/http://www.gainesville.com/article/20100323/articles/100329755|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NYU"/>他在高中时期对[[创意写作|创意写作]]产生了兴趣，并表示：“我将把毕生精力投入其中（指创意写作）……这是我最在乎的，也将是我未来的事业方向。”1996年，萨姆伯格从{{link-en|伯克利高中|Berkeley High School (Berkeley, California)}}毕业。<ref name="Q & A">{{cite web|url=http://dailynorthwestern.com/2008/04/15/archive-manual/q-a-with-andy-samberg/|title=Q&A with Andy Samberg|last=Salter|first=Christina|date=April 15, 2008|accessdate=April 26, 2013|work=The Daily Northwestern|archive-date=2015-09-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150923004552/http://dailynorthwestern.com/2008/04/15/archive-manual/q-a-with-andy-samberg/|dead-url=no}}</ref>之后他被[[加利福尼亞大學聖塔克魯茲分校|加利福尼亞大學聖塔克魯茲分校]]录取，两年后转学到了[[纽约大学|纽约大学]]。2000年，萨姆伯格从纽约大学毕业。<ref name="NYU">{{cite web|url=http://www.nyu.edu/alumni.magazine/issue10/10_culture_snl.html|publisher=[[纽约大学|NYU]]|title=Alumni Magazine > Culture > Live From New York, It's…|access-date=2014-02-17|archive-date=2010-05-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100530061407/http://www.nyu.edu/alumni.magazine/issue10/10_culture_snl.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

==事业==
萨姆伯格在大学期间主修电影，并拍摄了几部[[实验电影|实验电影]]，其中包括为{{link-en|詹姆斯·科查卡|James Kochalka}}的歌曲《猴子大战机器人》（{{lang|en|"Monkey vs. Robot"}}）拍摄的音乐录影带。萨姆伯格在这部录影带中饰演主角“猴子”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.playboy.com/playground/view/20q-andy-samberg|title=20Q: ANDY SAMBERG|publisher=[[Playboy|Playboy]]|author=Eric Spitznagel|date=2012-06-28|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20140221105412/http://www.playboy.com/playground/view/20q-andy-samberg|archivedate=2014-02-21|access-date=2014-02-17}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author= |url=http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I_QsCXm1vrk |title=Monkey vs. Robot |publisher=Youtube.com |date=25 November 2005 |accessdate=2011-07-24 |archive-date=2011-11-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120003733/http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=I_QsCXm1vrk |dead-url=no }}</ref>2000年，萨姆伯格与两位朋友{{link-en|阿齐瓦·沙弗|Akiva Schaffer}}和{{link-en|乔玛·塔科内|Jorma Taccone}}组建了{{link-en|寂寞孤岛乐队|The Lonely Island}}，三人一起拍摄制作自己的喜剧影片。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.elle.com/pop-culture/reviews/the-lonely-island-305509|title=Learn about Comedy Song Group Lonely Island Today|publisher=[[ELLE|ELLE]]|date=2009-03-02|access-date=2014-02-17|archive-date=2014-03-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140330013459/http://www.elle.com/pop-culture/reviews/the-lonely-island-305509|dead-url=no}}</ref>2005年，[[YouTube|YouTube]]成立后，三人的影片在网络上得以迅速传播，成为YouTube上的明星。好莱坞的经纪公司发现三人的才能之后与他们签下发展协议。<ref>Burns, Kelli S. Celeb 2.0: How Social Media Foster Our Fascination with Popular Culture. Santa Barbara, CA: Praeger/ABC-CLIO, 2009. Print.</ref>萨姆伯格在同年成为《[[周六夜现场|周六夜现场]]》节目的客座演员。而他在自己创办的喜剧网站[http://thelonelyisland.com/ TheLonelyIsland.com] {{Wayback|url=http://thelonelyisland.com/ |date=20210225100603 }}上主演的喜剧小品在一定程度上是促使他与经纪公司签约并最终进入《周六夜现场》节目组的重要因素。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.fastcompany.com/55984/target-dream-job | title=Target: Dream Job | publisher=Fast Company | date=2006-04-01 | accessdate=2014-02-16 | author=Rosenberg, Yuval | archive-date=2021-02-24 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210224135726/http://www.fastcompany.com/55984/target-dream-job | dead-url=no }}</ref>萨姆伯格加入《周六夜现场》之后仍然是寂寞孤岛乐队的成员之一，三人于2005年开始为节目撰写剧本。<ref name="snl">{{cite web | url=http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/06/11/andy-samberg-and-lonely-island-move-on-from-saturday-night-live.html | title=Andy Samberg and Lonely Island Move On From ‘Saturday Night Live’ | publisher=THE DAILY BEAST | date=2013-06-11 | accessdate=2014-02-16 | author=Fallon, Kevin | archive-date=2016-08-18 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160818232513/http://www.thedailybeast.com/articles/2013/06/11/andy-samberg-and-lonely-island-move-on-from-saturday-night-live.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>2009年，乐队发行了第一张专辑《{{link-en|Incredibad|Incredibad}}》。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.discogs.com/Lonely-Island-Incredibad/master/48531 | title=Lonely Island, The – Incredibad | publisher=Discog | accessdate=2014-02-16 | archive-date=2016-03-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160306051755/https://www.discogs.com/Lonely-Island-Incredibad/master/48531 | dead-url=no }}</ref>萨姆伯格之后在众多戏剧电影、商业广告、音乐录影带中出镜，并主持了包括[[2009年MTV電影大獎|2009年MTV電影大獎]]等在内的一系列活动。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20265861,00.html | title=Andy Samberg to Host MTV Movie Awards | publisher=[[人物_(雜誌)|People]] | date=2009-03-16 | accessdate=2014-02-16 | archive-date=2016-03-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105659/http://www.people.com/people/article/0,,20265861,00.html | dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年，萨姆伯格在[[哈佛大学|哈佛大学]]的毕业纪念日（{{lang|en|Class Day}}）上进行演讲。<ref name=HarvardSpeech>{{cite news|last=Lichter|first=Allison|title=Best College Speeches ’12: Samberg, Lynch, and Sorkin Sound Off|url=http://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2012/05/31/best-college-speeches-12-samberg-lynch-and-sorkin-sound-off/?mod=google_news_blog|accessdate=8 June 2012|newspaper=''[[Wall_Street_Journal|Wall Street Journal]]''|date=May 31, 2012|archive-date=2018-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613213716/https://blogs.wsj.com/speakeasy/2012/05/31/best-college-speeches-12-samberg-lynch-and-sorkin-sound-off/?mod=google_news_blog|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.harvard.edu/class-day-speakers | title=Class Day speakers at Harvard | publisher=[[哈佛大学|Harvard University]] | accessdate=2014-02-16 | archive-date=2015-08-01 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150801201050/http://www.harvard.edu/class-day-speakers | dead-url=no }}</ref>2012年9月，他主演了[[英国广播公司第三台|BBC第三台]]的喜剧《{{link-en|布谷鸟 (电视剧)|Cuckoo (TV series)|布谷鸟}}》，在其中饰演戴尔·艾希布里克（{{lang|en|Dale Ashbrick}}）一角。<ref>{{cite web|first=Hannah J|last=Davies|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2012/oct/23/cuckoo-surreal-subversive-sitcom|title=Have you been watching … Cuckoo|publisher=DC comics.com|date=October 23, 2012|accessdate=November 4, 2012|archive-date=2013-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130215095440/http://www.guardian.co.uk/tv-and-radio/tvandradioblog/2012/oct/23/cuckoo-surreal-subversive-sitcom|dead-url=no}}</ref>萨姆伯格还曾与[[亞當·山德勒|亞當·山德勒]]两次合作，出演了电影《[[爸爸的好儿子|爸爸的好儿子]]》（2012年）和《[[精灵旅社|精灵旅社]]》（2012年）。2013年，萨姆伯格制作了一部情景喜剧《[[神烦警察|神烦警察]]》并在其中担任主演。这部喜剧于2013年9月17日开始在[[福克斯广播公司|福克斯广播公司]]播出。<ref>{{cite web|last=Evans|first=Bradford|title=Andy Samberg's Fox Cop Show Has a Name: 'Brooklyn 99'|url=http://splitsider.com/2013/04/andy-sambergs-fox-cop-show-has-a-name-brooklyn-99/|work=Splitsider|accessdate=May 14, 2013|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608052016/http://splitsider.com/2013/04/andy-sambergs-fox-cop-show-has-a-name-brooklyn-99/|archive-date=2013-06-08|dead-url=yes}}</ref>2014年初，这部喜剧获得[[第71屆金球獎|第71屆金球獎]]“最佳音乐或喜剧类电视剧”，萨姆伯格也凭借在剧中的表现获得“最佳音乐或喜剧类电视剧男主角”。<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/tvshowbiz/article-2538499/Golden-Globes-2014-Andy-Samberg-hide-shock-Brooklyn-Nine-Nine-home-TWO-Golden-Globes-just-one-season.html | title='I didn't prepare anything!': Andy Samberg can't hide shock as Brooklyn Nine-Nine take home TWO Golden Globes after just one